    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  游戏故事背景简介</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本可以避免的灾难引发了几乎毁灭人类的连锁反应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽管全人类联合抗灾，但将近20个年头过去了，灾害仍然肆虐……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在被刚纳入抗灾计划不久的城市——SG01，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“我”想要维持和“她”共有的“稳固”生活，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但抗灾计划的人员分配要求却与“我”的想法产生了冲突。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而且，不止于此……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自2074年4月9日开始的诸多异常事件，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透露出这一切背后更大的阴谋与博弈……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人物介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/f5573da95c26b8ec00fc8ab9f78adfa3.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=466 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/2f1ab1a138e46f215aa73fbf02f6588b.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=466 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/4d1365d2b530263bf35aaabd0a3217e0.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=466 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/67dedf7063ec51b5c517c4650ab19b7d.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=466 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/ccd577f28f70232ff21b9bc1a66a6407.avif?t=1755312799\" width=616 height=466 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《人类终结之日——2074》是一款科幻悬疑AVG游戏，通过阅读文本、点击选项、收集文本，以及主动和被动地触发游戏机制来推动剧情。本游戏是一款剧情驱动的AVG游戏，拥有多个不同的角色视角，同时也带有文本收集，和少量的探索要素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>简单易用的UI</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/52214dfd2bfd580ea02a264c22f7c035.avif?t=1755312799\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras_big/52214dfd2bfd580ea02a264c22f7c035.avif?t=1755312799 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>文本收集要素</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/5b428ffa661f428c5c4fb3ec8cb3b402.avif?t=1755312799\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras_big/5b428ffa661f428c5c4fb3ec8cb3b402.avif?t=1755312799 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富的选择肢</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras/cc856102d055596be958afbf2cfc422f.avif?t=1755312799\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172420/extras_big/cc856102d055596be958afbf2cfc422f.avif?t=1755312799 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >P.S.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于是同人制作，本游戏受限于制作水平和体量，可能存在一些bug和文本校对的问题。如果出现了bug、文本问题，或使用的免费素材违反了使用规约、协议，请向作者反馈，作者会第一时间对反馈的bug进行修复，或删除违反使用规约的素材。</p>",
